    "data": [
        [
            [
                "Dialogue"
            ],
            [
                "Awesome [tn], and just in time. The event is about to start, so let me give you a quick tip: On your table, you’ll have a red and a green flag."
            ],
            [
                "The green flag is for all the people you match and feel attracted to! Click it at the end of your quick date, and these people will be added to your ‘Prospect list.’"
            ],
            [
                "The red flag is for people who you don’t match with. Click it and they won’t be saved to your list."
            ],
            [
                "If you feel nervous, remember that I won’t be far away! And [tn], I recommend you choose well… Getting into a relationship isn’t something to rush."
            ],
            [
                "So take your time getting to know the people here, and even if you don’t find anybody, remember"
            ],
            [
                "Suddenly, a high-pitched bell announced the beginning of the event. Helpie hurriedly gave me a thumbs up and I signaled them to walk back to give me some space."
            ],
            [
                "Soon after, people began sitting on tables as I waited patiently for someone to approach me. But of course, everybody is just walking past little ‘ol me."
            ],
            [
                "‘Why did I even come here?’ I thought as I get up from my seat. Suddenly, a tall, scruffy person sits at my table."
            ],
            [
                "They didn’t seem to care much about their appearance but still had that something in them."
            ],
            [
                "“Oh sorry, were you leaving?”"
            ],
            [
                "I look at their nametag, ‘Fabián’. What a unique name. Wait, Fabián? Have I heard this name before? Something in this person rang within me, but I wasn’t sure why."
            ],
            [
                "“No! Not at all. I was just stretching.”"
            ],
            [
                "I quickly pretended to stretch and sat back down in a heartbeat. I hope my nervous smile doesn’t show that I was close to giving up."
            ],
            [
                "“Say, nice to meet ya. I’m Fabián. And you?”"
            ],
            [
                "“My name is [tn]… as you can see on my nametag.”"
            ],
            [
                "Fabián looked intently at my nametag, just to pull away with a grin."
            ],
            [
                "“Sorry, I can’t read.”"
            ],
            [
                "“What? And… how did you register for this event?”"
            ],
            [
                "“C’mon, I’m pulling your leg. Of course I know how to read, duh!”"
            ],
            [
                "“Yeah, makes sense after all.” Still, I couldn’t help but feel the heat rise on my cheeks as I reproached myself for believing him."
            ],
            [
                "“Yeah… o-of course I knew. Like—how could you not read? Duh! Haha! I’m an idiot.”"
            ],
            [
                "I see how Fabián’s eyes light up as he looks at my phone case. Was he a connoisseur of good gaming titles?"
            ],
            [
                "“Wait… Is that a Moki Moki writing club phone case? Oh my, I love that game!”"
            ],
            [
                "“Yes, that’s it! I had never met any other fan before! Although I see you’re quite a fan of other games too.”"
            ],
            [
                "“Yeah, I am. Videogames are my escape, you know? After studying hard all day, there’s nothing better than gaming for a while and just enjoying myself.”"
            ],
            [
                "These were great news. He likes videogames just as I do. He better not be toxic when playing Valofang."
            ],
            [
                "“This is amazing! We should totally play together sometime! My Geekord nametag is—”"
            ],
            [
                "And that stupid bell rang. I wanted to strangle the organizers for ruining this moment, but then Fabián tapped my shoulder and passed me a note as he got up."
            ],
            [
                "“My Geekord nametag is in there. I’ll play any shooter or MOBA game with you if you’d like.”"
            ],
            [
                "I smile at Fabián as I see him walk away. This event was going much better than I had ever expected."
            ],
            [
                "Is Fabián a green or a red flag?"
            ],
            [
                "As I see Fabián walking away, I notice a patch on their backpack. It says “Aukademi’s D&D club”. Ain’t no way… this dude goes to my same uni?"
            ],
            [
                "That’s why it sounded so familiar. The universe really likes to do some crazy coincidences."
            ],
            [
                "The event kept going on, but talking with Fabián was more than enough. I went up to Helpie to tell them about my prospect list."
            ],
            [
                "“[tn], you’re back! I see you have something written on your list. Who are the lucky ones?”"
            ],
            [
                "“It’s only one… Fabián. I think I really got along with him, so… yeah. I think they’re the one I want to date.”"
            ],
            [
                "“Say no more! I’ll help you arrange everything so… get ready for your date!”"
            ],
            [
                "I can’t believe it. This is really happening! Your first date with someone you actually liked. This day was just getting better and better."
            ],
            [
                "For now… it was time to change into something nicer, and go for a proper date with Fabián…"
            ],
            [
                "I quickly run back to my house and put on one of my nicest outfits. I know Helpie is taking care of the arrangements, so I just focus on looking my best."
            ],
            [
                "I wait for a little while until Helpie calls me."
            ],
            [
                "“Everything is set up [tn]. Fabián will be waiting for you at the park. I heard they’ve got a surprise for youuu.”"
            ],
            [
                "My heart thumped rapidly as I heard the last part. And with that, I leave towards the park."
            ],
            [
                "The sun shines as I arrive and begin looking for Fabián. The park is filled with beautiful and tall trees, with plenty of places to sit and relax."
            ],
            [
                "Maybe it would have been nice to meet up in a specific place, but oh well. I look around, trying to figure out where my date could be."
            ],
            [
                "When suddenly, I feel two hands grab me by the shoulders."
            ],
            [
                "“Boo!”"
            ],
            [
                "“AAAAAAHH!!!!”"
            ],
            [
                "I turn around and just find Fabián’s cheeky grin, smiling at me."
            ],
            [
                "“Hahaha! Look at your face! I wish I had a camera on me right now.”"
            ],
            [
                "I rolled my eyes, but still found myself chuckling at the joke."
            ],
            [
                "“Welp, I’m glad you could make it. I don’t know if Helpie told you, but I’ve got something prepared for you. So… let’s get walking.”"
            ],
            [
                "As we walk, we find ourselves in comfortable silence. Still, I really want to get to know Fabián, and this was the perfect opportunity to do so."
            ],
            [
                "“So, Fabián… what’s up with the D&D patch?”"
            ],
            [
                "“Oh? The ‘Aukademi D&D club’ one? Well, it used to be a club at my uni. Unfortunately, it disbanded due to a lack of members.”"
            ],
            [
                "“Although, it wasn’t all that fun, you know? The members just couldn’t understand my complex storylines and preferred the basic ones more.”"
            ],
            [
                "No way… Fabián goes to Aukademi, my uni! The world is way too small."
            ],
            [
                "“Wait, you go to Aukademi? I study there too! What are you studying?”"
            ],
            [
                "“Game engineering and design. How about you?”"
            ],
            [
                "“What?!?! Me too!!! I—This is amazing! We should totally help each other now!”"
            ],
            [
                "Fabián nodded as I was excited about this discovery. I wasn’t surprised about not seeing him before; the class was fairly big."
            ],
            [
                "I was thinking of asking Fabián more questions about school, when suddenly he jogs to stand in front of me and makes me cover my eyes."
            ],
            [
                "“Wha-? What’s going on?”"
            ],
            [
                "“We’re getting close, so… bear with me.”"
            ],
            [
                "I huff, but ultimately decide to follow Fabián. We carefully walk for a little bit until he tells me to stop."
            ],
            [
                "“Alright, it’s not much but… I hope you like it.”"
            ],
            [
                "Fabián takes my hands off, and I see it. The sun shines as bright as ever, as I see Fabián’s surprise."
            ],
            [
                "And I really couldn’t help but feel my heart skip a beat as I saw what they had prepared for me…"
            ],
            [
                "“Thanks for playing our demo!”"
            ]
        ],
